skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Business success hinges on you having the right mindset. And who better to learn how to become a BOSS in Business than a former Dominatrix? 

The archetype of the dominatrix teaches us how to embrace the barrage of judgment that comes as we become more visible, while also teaching us what it means to be truly confident. 

The dominatrix holds the key for fierce self-love while also standing firmly in our expertise so that we attract clients like a magnet and grow a business with ease.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
